snippet.title: ZpellCatz Trailer June 2022 - Magical Action RPG with Cats
snippet.description:
Wishlist & Follow on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1447700?utm_source=youtube

The upcoming game by SimaGames is ZpellCatz, a magical Action RPG set in a colorful fantasy world. You are a cat with magic powers, stranded on a cursed island. Spiteful dogs are lurking in every corner and a fateful evil is about to emerge from the darkness.
